{"tid":1685333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全世界即刻整］全民set 連登嘅緊急登出密碼！！！","createTime":"2019-10-31T13:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:26:19.000Z","uid":231234,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"24d986e4172686a0483b733e159a6694e8b4a39a","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"用途：幫你喺非自願解鎖連登時救你一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，強制登出連登ac，以防有心人用你連登ac扮你本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如你被逼解鎖，請用緊急登出密碼！<br />\n記住，你只要扮本身就登出咗或者係你本身就冇ac就可以！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教學：首先要開啟呢個功能，設定&gt;密碼保護，<br />\nset 「保護密碼」（即係開apps密碼）同埋「緊急登出密碼」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你輸入保護密碼&gt;正常開連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但輸入緊急登出密碼&gt;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻自動登出連登</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n並將呢個密碼變成你嘅開apps密碼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人建議，當然保護密碼唔好係手機密碼，生日日期啦。<br />\n<br />\n但係我建議「緊急登出密碼」最好係生日日期！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解？係因為拎咗你手機嘅人可能會想入你連登ac達成某啲目的，甚至乎拎住你身份證，用你生日日期撞你密碼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢只要一入生日日期就幫你登出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如你被逼解鎖，請用緊急登出密碼！<br />\n記住，你只要扮本身就登出咗或者係你本身就冇ac就可以！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97b8b80b5a6ccdcf05cb6b5cb1d9bceb5783d69","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fo2u6cB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFo2u6cB.png&h=a407d34e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOOBMcB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOOBMcB.png&h=09b27ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hvz5ExD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvz5ExD.png&h=49ad19ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d28e36ea54d6a23cc25ac4a606da1630723d5ca","tid":1685333,"uid":94863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b225447e709a323fea4beed4bda9b87c17de181c","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"緊急登出密碼"},{"pid":"d78c2c1fb9950bfa45df9e2096e64893d40fe398","tid":1685333,"uid":157597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c26dc2a26a00a200b3f81c0f0a47d387f0706402","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:11:50.000Z","msg":"緊急登出密碼"},{"pid":"1eb51c6cb9b08ba19d42b33b3fbaeadcfce7cf59","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"緊急登出密碼"},{"pid":"47536f77d108a29468a9cf8660a2eb04461bf87b","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"緊急登出密碼"},{"pid":"d281ce81d01fd0c08158698fee84dc172b6abc7a","tid":1685333,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"緊急登出密碼"},{"pid":"6aa45dcd31ba9e46a69ea1fabe13f5d258e6e10b","tid":1685333,"uid":28601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"有用<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"fd230fb74681057111229b9f907150c450469985","tid":1685333,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislik